snippet.title: Homeboy's Got Receipts
snippet.description: Homeboy's Got Receipts is my laidback channel where I livestream about topics that I feel worth discussing, but haven't got the time to do a deep dive into as I would on my other channel (@Edwin's Generation). Within a week or so after going live, I try to get a recap of the show edited down to upload for those who missed it as the livestreams can be quite long and I don't want to clog up the channel. I feel the live shows are a great experience and time to chat and connect with the audience.
